---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Use"
  description="Terms of use for [C3_NAME] apps."
>

<section style="padding:3rem 1.5rem 1rem;">
  <div class="content">
    <p class="section-label">Legal</p>
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section legal-page" style="padding-top:1rem;">
  <div class="content">
    <p class="effective-date">Effective date: February 26, 2026</p>

    <p>
      These Terms of Use (&ldquo;Terms&rdquo;) govern your use of apps and
      services provided by [C3_NAME], a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization
      (&ldquo;we,&rdquo; &ldquo;us,&rdquo; or &ldquo;our&rdquo;). By downloading
      or using our apps, you agree to these Terms.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Use of Our Apps</h2>
    <p>
      Our apps are provided free of charge for personal, non-commercial use.
      You may use them to capture, organize, and compile personal media
      for yourself and your family.
    </p>
    <p>
      You agree not to use our apps to:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Record individuals without their knowledge or consent</li>
      <li>Store or distribute content that is illegal in your jurisdiction</li>
      <li>Attempt to reverse engineer or tamper with the app beyond what
          the open-source license permits</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. Open Source License</h2>
    <p>
      Our apps are released under the
      <a href="https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT">MIT License</a>.
      The source code is available at
      <a href="https://github.com/[C3_DOMAIN]">github.com/[C3_DOMAIN]</a>.
      The MIT License permits you to use, copy, modify, merge, publish,
      distribute, sublicense, and sell copies of the software, subject to
      the conditions of that license.
    </p>

    <h2>3. No Warranty</h2>
    <p>
      Our apps are provided &ldquo;as is&rdquo; without warranty of any kind.
      We make no guarantees about availability, accuracy, or fitness for any
      particular purpose. Use them at your own risk.
    </p>
    <p>
      We strongly recommend maintaining your own backups of important media.
      Use the built-in backup feature regularly.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>
      To the fullest extent permitted by law, [C3_NAME] shall not be liable
      for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising
      from your use of our apps, including loss of data.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      Your privacy is a core commitment. See our
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> for details on how our apps
      handle data.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Changes to These Terms</h2>
    <p>
      We may update these Terms as needed. Material changes will be noted
      with an updated effective date. Continued use of our apps after an
      update constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about these Terms:
      <a href="mailto:hello@[C3_DOMAIN].org">hello@[C3_DOMAIN].org</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
